# OpenCode's Glob/Grep tools are ripgrep-backed and respect .gitignore by default
# (see https://github.com/anomalyco/opencode/issues/31994 - no config toggle exists yet).
# These vault/ subdirectories are intentionally gitignored (transient/high-churn runtime
# state, or real personal data we don't want in git history), but the agent still needs
# to see them at runtime to do its job. Re-include them here without changing what git
# actually tracks. If you gitignore another vault/ path the agent needs to read, add it
# here too, or the agent will silently see it as empty.
!vault/Needs_Action/
!vault/Needs_Action/**
!vault/Logs/
!vault/Logs/**
!vault/Pending_Approval/
!vault/Pending_Approval/**
!vault/Approved/
!vault/Approved/**
!vault/Done/
!vault/Done/**
!vault/Rejected/
!vault/Rejected/**
!vault/Briefings/
!vault/Briefings/**
!vault/Plans/
!vault/Plans/**
